    {
      "id": "text_governance",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1384,
      "y": 154,
      "width": 326,
      "height": 638,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 150,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1050,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Contratos e regras que seguram a arquitetura\n\nEvidence-first\n- Evidence = fontes publicas da startup\n- Citation = fontes oficiais NVIDIA\n- unknown nunca vira suposicao\n- conflito vai para briefing/review\n\nSchemas versionados\n- startup_profile.v1\n- ai_native_assessment.v1\n- nvidia_knowledge.v1\n- nvidia_recommendation.v1\n- executive_briefing.v1\n- human_review_briefing.v1\n\nQuality gates\n- collection_quality\n- ready_for_recommendation\n- ready_for_briefing\n- human_review_requested\n\nLLM safety\n- Groq/LiteLLM so redige briefing\n- nao classifica fatos\n- nao escolhe tecnologia NVIDIA\n- prompt usa artefatos validados\n- sem segredo em payload/log\n\nDefault suite\n- pytest, ruff, mypy\n- sem rede\n- sem credenciais\n- sem Postgres real\n- sem browser real\n- sem LLM/embedding real",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Contratos e regras que seguram a arquitetura\n\nEvidence-first\n- Evidence = fontes publicas da startup\n- Citation = fontes oficiais NVIDIA\n- unknown nunca vira suposicao\n- conflito vai para briefing/review\n\nSchemas versionados\n- startup_profile.v1\n- ai_native_assessment.v1\n- nvidia_knowledge.v1\n- nvidia_recommendation.v1\n- executive_briefing.v1\n- human_review_briefing.v1\n\nQuality gates\n- collection_quality\n- ready_for_recommendation\n- ready_for_briefing\n- human_review_requested\n\nLLM safety\n- Groq/LiteLLM so redige briefing\n- nao classifica fatos\n- nao escolhe tecnologia NVIDIA\n- prompt usa artefatos validados\n- sem segredo em payload/log\n\nDefault suite\n- pytest, ruff, mypy\n- sem rede\n- sem credenciais\n- sem Postgres real\n- sem browser real\n- sem LLM/embedding real",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
